		{"id":"func_word","type":"text","text":"📄 **L1 · 文档输出**\n\n`kindergarten_template_cleaner.py`\n\n模板填充 → 输出：\n· **.docx**（主要）\n· .pdf（能力存在）\n· 图片PNG\n  （按接口暴露）\n\n⚠️ Word为主","x":160,"y":430,"width":200,"height":270,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"func_card","type":"text","text":"🎟 **L1 · 卡密系统**\n\n`/redeem`\n\n① 输入兑换码\n② 查GCS卡密池\n③ 验证有效性\n④ 写入Firestore\n⑤ 开通使用权限","x":380,"y":430,"width":200,"height":270,"color":"1"},
